# Task 4: Dashboard Design

## Objective
To design an interactive dashboard for business stakeholders using Power BI.

## Tool Used
- Power BI

## Dataset
- Superstore Sales Dataset

## Dashboard Features
- Sales and profit overview
- Region-wise and category-wise analysis
- Monthly sales trends
- Top 5 products by sales
- Interactive slicers for filtering

## Deliverables
- Power BI Dashboard
- Dashboard Screenshots
- PPT Summary

## Outcome
The dashboard provides clear and interactive business insights to support decision-making.


